title: The Music of Namaste Yoga by Tim McCauley [FLAC]
description:
You can now take the tranquility and calm of the Namaste soundtrack off the mat. The Music of Namaste features eleven full length compositions originally created for the television series. Over 70 minutes of instrumental music - all written to the rhythm of breathing. Use it for your own Yoga practice or just to find calm at the end of a long day. The Music of Namaste is composed and performed by Tim McCauley.
